{"tid":1795795,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國金融時報選出「be water」為年度字詞","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:33:46.000Z","uid":128430,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b3ca36393b7c664bc4a2ed6d048b1456db1a7c","tid":1795795,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》發表評論文章，選出「be water」為其中一個年度字詞。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，已故武打巨星李小龍這句名言，成為今年香港抗爭者的策略。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，受到「be water」理念影響，抗爭者「如露」般堵塞主要道路或者包圍重要建築物；而當防暴警察集結驅散時，他們已經「如霧」地四散，「如水」一樣往橫街窄巷逃走；但一旦被捕，抗爭者就「如冰」地頑抗。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，這個理念影響到世界各地的抗爭者，由西班牙、智利到黎巴嫩，都借鏡港人的「be water」策略。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍在1970年代接受訪問時，解釋自己武術哲學，大意清空自己，像水一樣不受型態限制，在不同時候變化，作出流動或者攻擊，像水一樣既柔且剛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚尖沙咀見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPaDLbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPaDLbc.jpg&h=c835051e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5391HXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5391HXZ.jpg&h=201dcc9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b39cef33d6f0bacf5781e2a74248144b4097e3e","tid":1795795,"uid":128430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTTYLby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTTYLby.png&h=3b3a02b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40b79e2dae97f396d553a30077c4442967d7e562","tid":1795795,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a8605a2699e188dbe1723b1c54189b493df11b9a","tid":1795795,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdc7731876ed0b942f628641035ce